<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>I would like to suggest to add additional parameter to Zend_Soap_AutoDiscover::handle() method that would be passed directly to $this-&gt;_wsdl-&gt;dump()
It could be usefull for, for instance, caching purposes. You can generate wsdl file once and then just read it from file. In fact maybe it's possible to replace current parameter $request becouse it's not used.</p>

<pre class="highlight"><code>
public function handle($filename = false)
{
    if (!$filename &amp;&amp; !headers_sent()) {
        header('Content-Type: text/xml');
    }
    $this-&gt;_wsdl-&gt;dump($filename);
}
</code></pre>

